OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy day to come
OL,6,Fwith occasional rain spreading north.
OL,7,FStaying quite cloudy but becoming
OL,8,Fsomewhat drier for a time later in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Windy around the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will remain cloudy through
OL,12,Fthe evening and overnight with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, heavy at times.
OL,14,FWindy around the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FCloud and rain, some heavy,
OL,17,Fpush northeast in the morning. Then
OL,18,Fshowers, some heavy and thundery,
OL,19,Ffollowing in the afternoon. Windy at
OL,20,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
