OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBright spells and some showers on
OL,7,FThursday. A further rain band pushes
OL,8,Fnortheast Friday morning, with showers
OL,9,Ffollowing. Showers or longer spells of
OL,10,Frain on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
